A state of re framing/restructuring the waves/energy
==============================================
Each and every form of energy are in under process/streaming at non delectable speed. Our activity are not simply look like in process but the activity is the resultant of unlimited number of waves movement. It is not possible to detected the waves in the form of stream but we can detect in the form of its state for observation purpose.

Our senses/mind/intellect are mainly responsible to create/recreate the waves for stability of life energy/instance of live energy. It is just like your hand and mouth is responsible to eat the food for stability/sustain of body similar ways our senses/mind/intellect are responsible to create the waves for stability of life ie for happiness/satisfaction/entertainment.

Every thing process with their nature only, if any energy have low intensity then it process to interact with low intensity energy ie..each and every state of energy proceed
for interact with similar state of energy.

What is re framing/restructuring of waves/energy?
-------------------------------------------
When any waves/energy flow it seems to get more stability only and at the time of starting flow it have some structure/frame with that it proceed. The current state of structure of waves framed in such a way that it seems to be maximum stability when it interact with similar state of waves but what happen when waves realize at intermediate of its flow the current structure/frame of wave will not maximize the stability? at this time waves/energy suddenly reach into next inner structuring/framing process and it framed/structured
the current state into some new structure so that it can find maximum stability with interaction.

***Framing/restructuring of waves is the intermediate/dynamic action taken by waves for maximizing its stability during interaction***

Ex-
1:-
When you going to take food, when you stated taking it and during eating you realize there is less salt in it then you put little more salt since you realize if we will put
little more salt then the food become more testy.
Here there is some expectation for the test of food is nothing but the starting state of waves but when during taking launch you realize less salt and you put little more salt is nothing but restructuring/re framing of you expectation towards test.

2:-
When you fly kite(a entertainment for mind but how the waves flow) and you see some another kite far away from your kite, if you seems to screw with another kite, then you
give more thread(starting state of waves emerge from mind), when your kite reach near to another kite, you put on their thread or you give chance to put on your thread is nothing
but the structuring/framing of waves. If realize if you put your thread is more stability then you put otherwise you give them a chance to put on your thread.
Or whatever you take action during screw is nothing but the dynamic state of framing of your stability of waves.

3:-
When you start some action with some plane(current structure of waves) but when you realize at intermediate you need to change something for more stability then you change
the some part of old plane is nothing but framing/restructuring of wages/plane.

4:-
When water fall from hill, where it realize more pulling sensitivity towards down it move in that direction but when there is a stone come in front of its flow it change the direction
of its flow.The changing the direction of flow is nothing but restructuring of flow.

***Re framing/restructuring of structure of waves is nothing but its nature at intermediate state of flow for maximize its stability***
